column6: We'd rather these be two separate proposals, as we'd vote YES" for the Uniswap v4 incentives
column7: but abstain for further refinement of the Unichain incentives. However
column8: we recognize that there wouldn't be any value in UNI without Uniswap Labs
column9: and that Unichain's and Uniswap on Unichain would benefit the rest of the Uniswap ecosystem. We'll be watching closely for the $11b in cumulative Uniswap swap volume to be hit."
